text: Turnpike Lane tube station is a station at Turnpike Lane on the Piccadilly Line of the London Underground, between Manor House and Wood Green stations, and in Travelcard Zone 3. ==References== ==Other websites== *Architectural history and photograph of Turnpike Lane in 1932 from the Royal Institute of British Architects Category:Piccadilly line stations Category:Transport architecture in London Category:Tube stations in the London Borough of Haringey Category:Railway stations opened in 1932 Category:Charles Holden buildings
title: Turnpike Lane tube station
